## Flow (`flow.json`)

`api_steps` lists the requests replayed in order. Each references a HAR entry by
`har_entry_index` (0-based into `data/session.har`), so `replay_api.py` reissues
the exact recorded request with live cookies/headers, only swapping your knobs.

%%FLOW_STEPS_TABLE%%

`replay_api.py` reissues every step by default. Use `--only-primary` to run just
the primary call. Mutating steps are refused unless `--confirm-mutating`.

