never prints them.

## UI replay contract

`variant.js` exports one async function; the runner supplies `page` (and a
`params` object from `PW_PARAMS`):

```js
module.exports = async (page, params) => {
  await page.goto("%%SOURCE_URL%%");
  // ... recorded steps with your inputs ...
};
```

`run_variant.js` launches a persistent Chrome context under a skill-local
profile (`<skill>/.browser-profile`), injects the embedded session cookies via
`har_auth.py`, records video, and closes the context (flushing the `.webm`).
`replay_ui.sh` converts it to `runs/<timestamp>/proof.mp4`.

Env: `PW_CHANNEL` (default `chrome`; `""` = bundled chromium), `PW_HEADLESS=1`,
`PW_PARAMS` (JSON passed to the variant), `PW_PROFILE`, `PW_TIMEOUT` (ms).

## Re-recording

If the embedded session expires (401/403 on replay), re-record the action with
the `generate-web-skills` skill and regenerate this skill.
